Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.96,0:00:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的話就用你的劍和你的「二刀流」來搶奪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能戰勝我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你盡可帶亞絲娜離開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.14,0:00:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過一旦落敗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就要加入血盟騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用劍說話正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.29,0:00:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用決鬥來了事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,{\fad(400,400)\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold\bord0\shad2}2024年10月20日 第75層 科里尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好位置所剩無幾 購票要從速
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21\fnMSungHK-Bold\fsp50}　{\fsp0}活傳說{\fsp70} {\fsp0}二刀流的惡魔\N{\fs36}希茲克利夫 VS 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲什麽要說出那種話來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 是我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.91,0:00:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就中了他的挑釁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.78,0:00:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前看桐人你使用二刀流的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你的強大已經到達了另一個次元
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但團長的獨特技能也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:49.78,*Default,NTP,0090,0000,0000,,{\fs28}Unique Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也曾在近距離看過幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻防自如的劍技「神聖劍」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:01:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊力自不必說 防禦力更尤具壓倒性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從未有人見過團長的HP值跌進黃色區域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的無敵已經超越了遊戲的平衡性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.39,0:01:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.95,0:01:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是打輸了 不僅我不能放假
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連桐人也必須加入血盟騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.59,0:01:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不覺得自己會輕易落敗

Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:39.70,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}認めてた臆病な過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:47.77,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}分からないままに怖がってた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:49.89,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}後ろの自分が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:56.72,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}現実を今に映す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.83,0:02:01.83,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}いくつもの空を描いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:03.89,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}ここはきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:09.37,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}儚い心 乱して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:15.08,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}夢で高く飛んだ躰は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:17.94,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}どんな不安纏っても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:19.98,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}振り払ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:24.42,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}眠る小さな想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:26.64,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}広がりだして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:28.70,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}気づく 弱い 私
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:35.40,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}君がいれば 暗い世界 強くいれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:41.16,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}長い夢見る心は そう 永遠で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:45.27,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:50.87,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I give you everything I have

Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:39.70,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}正視著膽怯的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:47.77,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}依然無法理解地畏懼著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:49.89,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}背後的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:56.72,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}此刻映照在現實中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.83,0:02:01.83,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}描繪了數片天空的此處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:03.89,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}一定是在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:09.37,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}亂我脆弱心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:15.08,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}乘著夢想高飛身軀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:17.94,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}無論有任何不安糾纏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:19.98,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}都掙脫前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:24.42,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}將沉睡著的小小的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:26.64,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}擴展開來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:28.70,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}意識到弱小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:35.40,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}只要有你在 黑暗的世界 也能一直堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:41.16,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}用沉眠許久的心 永遠堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:45.27,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:50.87,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I give you everything I have

